    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition and is recommended primarily as a restoration project or a donor car for parts. The exterior shows substantial wear, including visible rust patches, significant paint fading, and several noticeable dents. Mechanically, the car requires major repairs to be roadworthy, and the interior exhibits heavy wear with tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronic components. It is sold strictly as-is for an enthusiast ready for a challenge.",
